  "page": "Archon of Tyrosh (War of the Ninepenny Kings)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\"><img alt=\"Tyrosh.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/50px-Tyrosh.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/75px-Tyrosh.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/100px-Tyrosh.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Archon of Tyrosh</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\"><img alt=\"Tyrosh.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/50px-Tyrosh.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/75px-Tyrosh.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/100px-Tyrosh.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Archon_of_Tyrosh\" title=\"Archon of Tyrosh\">Archon of Tyrosh</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\">Tyroshi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nUnknown</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>This <b>Archon of Tyrosh</b>, was the ruler of <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\">Tyrosh</a> in the time preceding the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Ninepenny_Kings\" title=\"War of the Ninepenny Kings\">War of the Ninepenny Kings</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_jaehaerys_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_jaehaerys_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Archon_of_Tyrosh_(War_of_the_Ninepenny_Kings)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The ruling <a href=\"/index.php/Archon_of_Tyrosh\" title=\"Archon of Tyrosh\">Archon of Tyrosh</a> was deposed when the <a href=\"/index.php/Band_of_Nine\" title=\"Band of Nine\">Band of Nine</a> and its armies <a href=\"/index.php/Sack_of_Tyrosh\" title=\"Sack of Tyrosh\">sacked</a> Tyrosh at the behest of one of its members, the merchant prince <a href=\"/index.php/Alequo_Adarys\" title=\"Alequo Adarys\">Alequo Adarys</a>, was then installed as the ruler of the city. Adarys reigned until <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_266_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">266&#160;AC</a>, when he was poisoned by his queen. Afterward, the legitimate Archon was restored to power.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_jaehaerys_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_jaehaerys_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Archon_of_Tyrosh_(War_of_the_Ninepenny_Kings)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_jaehaerys_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_jaehaerys_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_jaehaerys_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Targaryen Kings: Jaehaerys II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404093216\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.067 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.276 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 492/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10461/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5065/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 588/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1049/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.190/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.46 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  268.247      1 -total\n 96.01%  257.548      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 95.32%  255.701      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.73%   31.471     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  5.44%   14.598      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.91%    5.129      2 Template:Ref\n  1.38%    3.695      1 Template:Date\n  1.13%    3.029      2 Template:Ref/core\n  0.60%    1.620      1 Template:References\n  0.34%    0.923      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wester